:04Z\",\n117:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n118:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n119:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n120:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n121:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3457#issuecomment-3001996375\",\n122:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n123:     }\n124:   ],\n125:   \"title\": \"Track the addition of VCCF vasculature terms here\",\n126:   \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3457\"\n127: }\n\n(End of file - total 127 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"body\": \"### Preferred term labels, synonyms, suggested definitions, references, parent terms\\n* The targeted terms and their labels, synonyms come from [this table.](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QrXvmsiCPqFQy6ZMHJQiE2rySrhmbQ1TE7GgDsg9ZFk/edit?gid=695544266#gid=695544266)\\n\\n### Priority organs\\n\\n```tsv\\n1.\\t eye\\n2.\\t heart\\n3.\\t kidney\\n4.\\t large intestine\\n5.\\t liver\\n6.\\t lung\\n7.\\t pancreas\\n8.\\t skin of body\\n9.\\t small intestine\\n10.\\t spleen \\n```\\n\\n### Remain be added\\n* as of [2024-12-24](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1zvY1smk9FvhPorn3raqQss7nYkEFQOOSfVGmBbwiLdQ/edit?gid=2125289498#gid=2125289498): **659**.\\n* as of [2025-01-09](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1zvY1smk9FvhPorn3raqQss7nYkEFQOOSfVGmBbwiLdQ/edit?gid=2125289498#gid=2125289498): **586**.\\n* as of [2025-01-27](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1zvY1smk9FvhPorn3raqQss7nYkEFQOOSfVGmBbwiLdQ/edit?gid=2125289498#gid=2125289498): **568**.\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\n  \"comments\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd86Yqm1_\",\n      \"author\": {\n        \"login\": \"rays22\"\n      },\n      \"authorAssociation\": \"COLLABORATOR\",\n      \"body\": \"### Mapping table of *380 vccf terms* that already exist in Uberon\\r\\n* as of [2024-12-24](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1zvY1smk9FvhPorn3raqQss7nYkEFQOOSfVGmBbwiLdQ/edit?gid=92781377#gid=92781377)\\r\\n\\r\\ndefined_class | label | map